<HEAD1>baiyer sImAnA periye </HEAD1>
<RIMG web="cover.jpg">baiyer malAT</RIMG>
 ei pAtAy AmAr @{<E>Real Analysis (Volume 1)</E>@}-er sange sampar+kita kichhu tathya pAbe, yeman 
kono bhul-truTi dharA paRle ekhAne seTA bale deba. aneke Ab~dAr kare thAko natun natun a.nka 
debAr janya. seguloo ekhAne deoyA yAbe. Ar yArA a.nka-Ta.nka likhe jAnAte chAo (bA kono mantabya
 karte chAo)   tAder janya nIche ekTA far+ma rayechhe. okhAne likhe dilei Ami imele peye yAba.    
yadi byak+tigata uttar chAo tabe tomAr imel dite pAro, naile Ami ei pAtAtei uttarTA diye rAkhbo, tumi samaymata dekhe nite
 pArbe.
<HEAD2>ekTu bojhAno</HEAD2>
ekjan chhAtrI chatur+tha adhyAyer @{<E>84</E>@}  nambar pAtAr a.nkaTA ekTu bojhAte balechhila. bhAblAm sei bARti bojhAnoTA 
anyaderao kAje lAgte pAre, tAi <LINK to="valentina.html">ekhAne</LINK>  tule dilAm. 
<HEAD2>ish.h</HEAD2> 
<HEAD3>chhApA paReni (ekhan Thik karA haye gechhe) </HEAD3>
pratham chhApAr samaye bAroTA pAtAy bA.nlA a.nshaTuku  ThikThAk chhApA hay ni. ekhan abashya
 segulo Thik kare neoyA hayechhe. nehAt yadi tomAr baiTA puronogulor ekTA hay tabe sei pAtAr 
sa.nkhyAgulo jAniye rAkhi@{<E>:</E>@}
<Q> @{<E>37,58,71,92,103,145,157,199,237,259,323</E>@} Ar @{<E>353.</E>@}</Q>
  ei pAtAgulo ekhAn theke <A href="badpages.pdf">DAunloD</A> 
kare nite pAro. 
ei bhulTA dharechhe sAyak. du.Hkher kathA @{<E>303</E>@}  nambar pAtAteo ekai samasyA Achhe. seTA
 jAn~te perechhi sujaymAdhab rAyer kAchhe theke, puro sa.nskaraNTA sheS haye yAoyAr pare! sei pAtATA  <LINK to="p303.pdf" >ekhAne</LINK> 
diye dilAm.
