<HEAD2>hAt pAkAnor a.nka</HEAD2>
AmAr baite Ami a.nka dii khub bechhe bechhe. biSaybas+tuTA bujhte yataTA lAge. ekTA 
biSay khAnikTA bujhei ek rAsh kaThin a.nker bhIRe taliye gele Thik kare shekhA hay nA. tabe 
ekbAr shekhA haye gele nAnA rakam a.nka kare hAt pAkAno bhAlo. erakam a.nkaoyAlA bhAlo baiyer
 kh,noj anekei AmAr kAchhe jAn~te chAo. tomrA @{<E>Kaczor</E>@} eba.n @{<E>Nowak</E>@}-er
 @{<E>Problems in Mathematical Analysis</E>@}  baigulo dekhte pAro. kayekTA khanDa Achhe baiTAr. pratiTA 
adhyAye nAnArakam a.nka eba.n adhyAyer sheSe tAder samAdhAn. namunA hisebe er dwitIya khanDer 
pratham adhyAyer prashnagulor <A href="KaczorNowak.pdf">tAlikATA ekhAne tule dilAm</A>. jAni nA
erakam bhAbe tule deoyATA Ain~sangata kinA. kAro Apatti thAkle jAnio, sariye deba.   
</NOTE>

